title: Banished Disciple’s Counterattack
description: You’re Reading Banished Disciple’s Counterattack At MANHUAUS.COM As a loyal disciple, Ye Chen dedicated himself to guard the spiritual medicine field for his sect. But, during a fight with enemies, the spiritual field was destroyed. His loyalty and dedicating to the sect could not save him. The loyalty he thought he had obtained from his peers and lover, could not save him from betrayal. Thus, he was shamelessly banished from the sect. With the help of a flame falling from heaven, Ye Chen began to develop himself into a stronger cultivator. Battled against his opponents, unfolded his legendary life and rewrote his own story… King of Martial Arts, Emperor Xianwu, Immortal Martial Emperor Venerable, Les Chroniques du disciple Dragon, 선무제존, 仙武帝尊, The Path of Conquest, Xianwu Dizun, Immortal and Martial Venerable Emperor
